data.description: Location, location, location!! A few finishing touches will make this 3 bdrm, 2 full bath ranch a perfect family home! Vinyl sided with 2 car garage (one under- perfect for work shop) Spacious living rm open to eat-in kit. hdwd floors, private deck off master bdrm, ample closets, AC and lots of sunny windows! This affordable house is located on desirable Street w/ cul-de-sac. Kitchen appl. to remain This is a great opportunity - don't miss out! Easy to show and seller can do quick closing!
data.whatILove: Custom shade in living room added in 2021. New water heater installed 2019. Kitchen renovated and expanded in 2018. Custom shade in kitchen added 2018. New furnace installed 2015. New room added to basement 2013.
